${goto 446} ● ${top name 2}${top cpu 2}
${goto 450} ● ${top name 3}${top cpu 3}
${goto 454} ● ${top name 4}${top cpu 4}
${goto 457} ● ${top name 5}${top cpu 5}
${goto 462}${voffset 200} RAM: $memperc%
${goto 458} $mem/$memmax 
